*Gospodin* je pokazao svoje veliko srce i obradovao sve prisutne. (The gentleman showed his big heart and made everyone present happy.)

Svi smo bili zahvalni *Gospodinu* za njegovu ljubaznost i poštovanje. (We were all thankful to the gentleman for his kindness and respect.)

Moj *gospodin* je zaista znao da prepozna pravo dobro. (My sir truly knew how to recognize true goodness.)

Uvek je bilo lako komunicirati sa *gospodinom* zbog njegovog otvorenog umu. (It was always easy to communicate with the gentleman due to his open mind.)

*Gospodina* je krasila čast i poštenje. (The gentleman was characterized by honor and integrity.)